Author: not_the_cicada
Text: I stupidly let my hands turn blue because I feel like it makes me more valid and it’s batshit insane and I hate it, wtf do I have to prove to myself or anyone else?   Hand warmers ftw.

Author: kiwi_487
Text: Been there, done that. Eds literally make you do the dumbest shit. I‘ve come to the conclusion, that I‘d rather be warm than to burn 5 extra calories. Life’s better on the warm side ✌🏻
